Components originating from KIRA-Slack (and remaining under the Apache License,
Version 2.0) include, among others: the agent runtime harness and Slack
integration, the message queueing infrastructure, the orchestrator/operator
agent, the memory and proactive-suggestion subsystems, and the difficulty-based
3-tier model routing, together with the web/desktop application scaffold.

